txt.en: 'There are many profitable things that can be found down here.'
'Ah yes, these should fetch a fine price.'
Eshéra has suggested you defeat crocodiles to collect their skins in Ilmabiri, beneath the Sail-haven of Umbar Baharbêl.
You have collected the skins of defeated crocodiles in the sewers beneath the Sail-haven of Umbar Baharbêl. You should bring them to Eshéra at Hêbatokh, her camp in Ilmabiri.
'Ah yes, these should fetch a fine price. Here is your cut. It is a pleasure doing business with you.'
Eshéra has a plan to make some extra coin for you both by selling crocodile skins to a dealer at the market in Umbar-môkh.

'There are many profitable things that can be found down here. If you are interested, the skins of crocodiles are also in demand. These I know they use to make shoes, bags and other items to sell to people in the Upper Ward with more money than sense. If you also bring me crocodile skins, there will be something in it for you.'
